'''Scavenger beasts''' are monsters found in the [[Chambers of Xeric]]. They are found in ruins and drop various items needed for puzzles and materials for skilling. They closely resemble [[Skavid|Skavids]] found in the [[Feldip Hills]] region of Kandarin, as they appeared prior to their [[Graphical updates (historical)|graphical update]] on 5 December 2006. They may be a subspecies of Skavid native to [[Mount Quidamortem]].

